{"tid":1342770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英今日表示年青人不學做人會遺害社會","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:04.000Z","uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"08bfa0d8633b5716428f5cb57bc9effe969c1e9e","tid":1342770,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:56:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1JB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=cc3c5c36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 新聞\t<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月21日 下午5:09<br />\n【Now新聞台】全國政協副主席梁振英出席一個新書發布會時，被問到年青人如何把握大灣區機遇，他認為年青人無論本領多高都應先學做人再學做事，否則會遺害社會。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英：「學校教得不多，在家庭父母太忙教得不多的就是教青少年學做人，先學做人然後學做事，一個人若只能夠學做事，他做事的本領無論有多強但他不學做人就不是一個好人，對社會的遺害很大，他的本領愈高對社會的遺害愈大。」"},{"pid":"0f7c47b39bba63944528796d873175a948e74e48","tid":1342770,"uid":65214,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"唔想理啲on9 唔好推thx"},{"pid":"700d8bfb1e6f2e629eecd4e8a0a1991870223ddf","tid":1342770,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:04.000Z","msg":"cy真係用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗班人真係讀得唔多書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}